{"thag7.2:0.1":"Theragatha 7.2 ","thag7.2:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thag7.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag7.2:0.4":"Lakundakabhaddiyattheragatha ","thag7.2:1.1":"“Pare ambatakarame, ","thag7.2:1.2":"vanasandamhi bhaddiyo; ","thag7.2:1.3":"Samulam tanhamabbuyha, ","thag7.2:1.4":"tattha bhaddova jhayati. ","thag7.2:2.1":"Ramanteke mudingehi, ","thag7.2:2.2":"vinahi panavehi ca; ","thag7.2:2.3":"Ahanca rukkhamulasmim, ","thag7.2:2.4":"rato buddhassa sasane. ","thag7.2:3.1":"Buddho ce me varam dajja, ","thag7.2:3.2":"so ca labbhetha me varo; ","thag7.2:3.3":"Ganheham sabbalokassa, ","thag7.2:3.4":"niccam kayagatam satim. ","thag7.2:4.1":"Ye mam rupena pamimsu, ","thag7.2:4.2":"ye ca ghosena anvagu; ","thag7.2:4.3":"Chandaragavasupeta, ","thag7.2:4.4":"na mam jananti te jana. ","thag7.2:5.1":"Ajjhattanca na janati, ","thag7.2:5.2":"bahiddha ca na passati; ","thag7.2:5.3":"Samantavarano balo, ","thag7.2:5.4":"sa ve ghosena vuyhati. ","thag7.2:6.1":"Ajjhattanca na janati, ","thag7.2:6.2":"bahiddha ca vipassati; ","thag7.2:6.3":"Bahiddha phaladassavi, ","thag7.2:6.4":"sopi ghosena vuyhati. ","thag7.2:7.1":"Ajjhattanca pajanati, ","thag7.2:7.2":"bahiddha ca vipassati; ","thag7.2:7.3":"Anavaranadassavi, ","thag7.2:7.4":"na so ghosena vuyhati”ti. ","thag7.2:7.5":"… Lakundakabhaddiyo thero …. "}